title: Artyom Yusupov
text:
Artyom Aleksandrovich Yusupov (; born 29 April 1997) is a Russian <a href="association%20football">football</a> player. He plays for <a href="FC%20Volgar%20Astrakhan">FC Volgar Astrakhan</a> on loan from <a href="FC%20Ural%20Yekaterinburg">FC Ural Yekaterinburg</a>.
Club career.
He made his debut in the <a href="Russian%20Premier%20League">Russian Premier League</a> for <a href="FC%20Ural%20Yekaterinburg">FC Ural Yekaterinburg</a> on 29 April 2017 in a game against <a href="FC%20Terek%20Grozny">FC Terek Grozny</a>.
On 27 January 2021, he joined <a href="FC%20Volgar%20Astrakhan">FC Volgar Astrakhan</a> on loan until the end of the 2020–21 season. On 10 June 2021, he returned to Volgar on a new loan for the 2021–22 season.
